One thing that i have noticed is whilst inrealm the pulses pulse steady for 9 seconds or so then 3 short fast burst, then back to pulsing steady. This is only on run speed that ive seen and not on any of the other songs, while out of realm the 3 fast pulses dissapear.<br>
I wish there were an option to make demos in this game it would show perfectly this juddery sh*t we call speed song. Btw im only lvl 38 so do not have last run song.<br>
