<br>
I can testify that neither bards OR minstrel suffer from this problem. I have a lvl 50 mincer on excal and a lvl 39 bard excal (both euro servers and i have 2 accounts) and a lvl 38 skald on prywden. I can run as long as i want with either bard or minstrel so long as i personally do not engage in combat or get fired at, or meleed, even if they are misses. So this is also a bug.<br>
